ZH: 你在我家做什么？滚蛋！
EN: What are you doing in my house? Get out!

ZH: 如果你再这样说我，我要让你滚蛋！
EN: If you speak to me like that again, I'll make you leave!

ZH: 这里没有你的位置，快点滚蛋！
EN: There's no place for you here, go away!

ZH: 孩子，别再捣乱了，滚蛋去学习吧！
EN: Child, stop messing around and go study!

ZH: 他总是挑衅我，我真想让他滚蛋！
EN: He always provokes me, I really want to make him go away!

ZH: 你给我找事吗？滚蛋！
EN: Are you trying to pick a fight with me? Get lost!

ZH: 不要再麻烦我了，滚蛋吧！
EN: Don't bother me anymore, go away!

ZH: 我不想和你说话，滚蛋！
EN: I don't want to talk to you, get lost!

ZH: 你这样做真是无耻，滚蛋吧！
EN: You're so shameless doing this, get out!

ZH: 这个地方不欢迎你，滚蛋！
EN: This place doesn't welcome you, get lost!

ZH: 我不需要你的帮助，滚蛋吧！
EN: I don't need your help, go away!

ZH: 你这个可恶的人，滚蛋去死吧！
EN: You despicable person, go to hell!

ZH: 别再缠着我了，快点滚蛋！
EN: Stop bothering me, go away quickly!

ZH: 没听明白吗？滚蛋！
EN: Didn't you understand? Get lost!

ZH: 若你再敢说话，我要让你滚蛋！
EN: If you dare to speak again, I'll make you leave!

ZH: 你有什么资格对我指手画脚？滚蛋吧！
EN: What authority do you have to meddle in my affairs? Go away!

ZH: 别再站在我面前，滚蛋吧！
EN: Don't stand in front of me anymore, get lost!

ZH: 这里没有你的位置，赶紧滚蛋！
EN: There's no place for you here, hurry up and leave!

ZH: 闭上你的臭嘴，滚蛋！
EN: Shut your filthy mouth, get out!

ZH: 你的存在只会给我带来麻烦，滚蛋吧！
EN: Your presence only brings me trouble, go away!
